OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter harassing ex-wife
OL,6,FA former Conservative MP who harassed
OL,7,Fher ex-wife has been handed a
OL,8,Fcommunity order.
OL,10,FKatie Wallis, 41, of Butetown,
OL,11,FCardiff, the MP for Bridgend in South
OL,12,FWales from 2019 to 2024, became the
OL,13,Ffirst openly transgender MP in the
OL,14,FHouse of Commons in 2022.
OL,16,FAppearing before Cardiff Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt on Monday, Wallis, who was
OL,18,Fpreviously known as Jamie, was
OL,19,Fsentenced for harassing her ex-wife,
OL,20,FRebecca Wallis, now known as Rebecca
OL,21,FLovell.
