OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter harassing ex-wife
OL,6,FThe court heard the former MP sent
OL,7,Fmessages accusing Ms Lovell of being
OL,8,F"mean" to them, demanding to know
OL,9,Fabout their new partner, saying she
OL,10,Fwas "cock hunting," and calling her a
OL,11,F"c***" and a "f****** bitch".
OL,13,FThe court heard how on February 25,
OL,14,Fusing an unknown number, the former MP
OL,15,Fdemanded #350,000 be put into their
OL,16,Fbank account within 15 minutes.
OL,18,FIn a separate message, Wallis referred
OL,19,Fto her ex-wife and father as
OL,20,F"prejudiced f******" adding they hope
OL,21,Fthey "never have a happy moment again".
