OL,6,FThe couple split in 2020, with the
OL,7,Fdivorce finalised in 2024.
OL,9,FIn a victim impact statement, which
OL,10,Fwas read to the court, Ms Lovell said:
OL,11,F"This is the hardest thing I have
OL,12,Fwritten, for so long I have had to
OL,13,Ffight against the tide of Jamie's
OL,14,Fbehaviour, publicly and privately."
OL,16,FShe added: "The woman I used to be is
OL,17,Fdestroyed. I will never understand
OL,18,Fwhat I have done to deserve the hurt I
OL,19,Fhave endured."
