OL,6,FMs Lovell described the last six
OL,7,Fmonths as "utterly devastating" and
OL,8,Fsaid she was living her life as an
OL,9,F"overstimulated adult constantly in
OL,10,Ffight or flight".
OL,12,FShe said she feared Wallis turning up
OL,13,Fat her home, leading her to have CCTV
OL,14,Finstalled.
OL,16,FWallis, who was wearing a black dress,
OL,17,Flooked down as the statement was read
OL,18,Fto the court.
