OL,6,FShe also said Wallis was suffering
OL,7,Ffrom PTSD, a depressive disorder and
OL,8,Fan adjustment disorder.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Rhys Williams handed
OL,11,FWallis a 12-month community order to
OL,12,Fbe carried out over 12 days and a fine
OL,13,Fworth #1,264.
OL,15,FWallis, who pleaded guilty to leaving
OL,16,Fthe messages at a hearing in June,
OL,17,Finitially denied the charges, but
OL,18,Fchanged her plea when allegations of
OL,19,Fhaving driven by her ex-wife's home
OL,20,Fwere removed from the charge.
